Package org.neo4j.values.storable

Class DurationValue

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.values.AnyValue
      • org.neo4j.values.storable.Value
        • org.neo4j.values.storable.ScalarValue
          • org.neo4j.values.storable.DurationValue
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Comparable<DurationValue>, TemporalAmount, Measurable
    public final class DurationValue
extends ScalarValue
implements TemporalAmount, Comparable<DurationValue>
    We use our own implementation because neither Duration nor Period fits our needs. Duration only works with seconds, assumes 24H days, and is unable to handle larger units than days. Period only works with units from days or larger, and does not deal with time.
